word_group.brief_definition: 国家锦标赛；全国冠军；全国锦标赛
争夺冠军；打进总决赛；冠军争夺战

bilingual.target: 他们赢得了锦标赛的冠军。

bilingual.source: He trained hard to fight in the championship.
bilingual.target: 他努力训练以在锦标赛中打架。

bilingual.source: She has won the championship three times in a row.
bilingual.target: 她已经连续三次赢得锦标赛。

bilingual.source: The athlete craved victory in the championship.
bilingual.target: 这位运动员渴望在锦标赛中获胜。
这名运动员在锦标赛中的表现不佳。

bilingual.source: The sports federation organized the annual championship.
bilingual.target: 体育联盟组织了年度锦标赛。

bilingual.source: The team returned home triumphant after the championship.
bilingual.target: 该队在锦标赛后胜利的回到家。

bilingual.source: They watched the eventing championship on television.
bilingual.target: 他们在电视上观看了三项赛锦标赛。

bilingual.source: The championship game will be held in the national stadium.
bilingual.target: 锦标赛比赛将在国家体育场举行。

bilingual.source: She competed in the national swimming championship last year.
bilingual.target: 她去年在全国游泳锦标赛中竞争。

yingyinNormal.en: If it's not to win a championship?
You know, I once scored 41 points at a league championship game. No way.
yingyinNormal.zh: 知道吗，我曾在联赛决赛里得了41分，不可能。

yingyinNormal.en: Just get me a little bit closer and I will get you that championship team.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再多给一点，我就能为你打造一支冠军队。

yingyinNormal.en: That's my bar. My bar is here. My bar is to take this team to the championship.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是我的目标，我的目标在这里，我的目标是让这支球队赢得冠军。

yingyinNormal.en: Sweetie, that's a highlight from the '98 championship game. Oh. Did not know that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的，现在放的是98年冠军赛的比赛集锦。我不知道。

yingyinNormal.en: The championship games, they don't come along all the time. They're something special.
yingyinNormal.zh: 冠军赛不是年年都能参加的，这次机会难得。

yingyinNormal.en: It wasn't until the 2006 AFC Championship when they played the Broncos. Do you remember? No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 直到2006年，美国橄榄球联盟冠军赛，他们跟丹佛野马队比赛，记得吗？不记得。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll forget about her. I'll forget the audition and we'll go out to get that championship. Everyone happy now?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我会忘了她，忘了试镜，我们会得到冠军，都满意了？

yingyinNormal.en: Who is gonna get their sorry butts kicked in Friday's championship game if Troy's worried about an audition? We are.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果特洛伊牵挂着试镜会，礼拜五的冠军赛谁会被打败？我们。

yingyinNormal.en: Billy, of the 20,000 notable players for us to consider, I believe that there is a championship team of 25 people that we can afford.
yingyinNormal.zh: 比利，在我们关注的两万名球员中肯定能找到我们承担得起的二十五人组建一支冠军队.

yingyinNormal.en: I always told myself my progression is gonna be Become a rotation player, become a starting point guard, And then win an NBA championship.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我一直对自己说，我的进步历程会是这样，从进入轮换，到成为首发控卫，然后赢得NBA总冠军

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I'm ready. I don't know if Stuart told you what you're up against tonight, but before you stands the co-captain of the East Texas Christian Youth Holy Roller Bowling League championship team. Seven to 12 year old division. Also, Penny's pretty good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然准备好了。我不知道斯图尔特有没有告诉你今晚你的对手是谁，不过站在你面前的人就是东德克萨斯州青年基督徒圣保龄同盟会冠军队的联盟队长，7到12岁参赛组。佩妮打得也不错。
